  "lines": [
    {
      "text": "-Elon Musk is making Neurolink",
      "start": 4636,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2200
    },
    {
      "text": "so people can talk to their pets.",
      "start": 4639,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2201
    },
    {
      "text": "\"Aww, now they can tell us just how much they love us.\"",
      "start": 4642,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2202
    },
    {
      "text": "\"I don't know, but I've thought about it fucking a lot.\"",
      "start": 4647,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 2203
    },
    {
      "text": "Imagine dog dads having the neuter talk.",
      "start": 4650,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2204
    },
    {
      "text": "After a painful conversation about cutting their balls off,",
      "start": 4654,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2205
    },
    {
      "text": "they'd be like, \"Please, Poppy,",
      "start": 4657,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2206
    },
    {
      "text": "I promise to keep my pecker in my pants.\"",
      "start": 4660,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 2207
    },
    {
      "text": "Dudes would be so traumatized,",
      "start": 4663,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2208
    },
    {
      "text": "they'd never neuter dogs ever again.",
      "start": 4665,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2209
    },
    {
      "text": "And the straight population would go way out of control.",
      "start": 4667,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 2210
    },
    {
      "text": "And if dogs didn't talk, they could understand TV.",
      "start": 4671,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2211
    },
    {
      "text": "Imagine coming home to find your dog",
      "start": 4674,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2212
    },
    {
      "text": "watching AOC on C-SPAN.",
      "start": 4676,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2213
    },
    {
      "text": "Poppy, she's so smart.",
      "start": 4680,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2214
    },
    {
      "text": "Next day, dog's on the doorstep of a shelter with a note.",
      "start": 4684,
      "label": "setup",
      "line_number": 2215
    },
    {
      "text": "Good dog, but he's a fucking Democrat.",
      "start": 4688,
      "label": "punchline",
      "line_number": 2216
    },
    {
      "text": "Thank you. I'm Luke Robinson.",
      "start": 4692,
      "label": "fluff",
      "line_number": 2217
    },
    {
      "text": "They call me your big dog. Thank you.",
      "start": 4694,
